{"tid":1181061,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"而家政府乜都有online form真係好方便 快啲一齊trytry佢啦","createTime":"2019-06-01T10:12:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-01T14:44:55.000Z","uid":30882,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"51ec2e6145a6db645260910e403f29f0c7f51a4d","tid":1181061,"uid":30882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T10:12:44.000Z","msg":"睇緊居屋網上申請 <br />\n見到而家正苦有效率左 介紹翻下面張form俾大家去篤下灰<br />\n反正又咁啱俾正苦DQ我個公屋application 都係時候要盡翻一個市民嘅責任<br />\n<br />\n如果你見到隔離左右 中左下面嘅情況 記得講俾正苦知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又或者有人自爆都可以share俾正苦 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1119955/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1119955/page/1</a><br />\n話哂交左稅唔係唔用下正苦服務啊下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n丟空單位 (或逾三個月非經常持續居於單位)<br />\n分租或轉租單位 (不論有沒有租金收入)<br />\n在單位內進行不法活動 (如聚賭、藏毒、藏有私煙等)<br />\n將單位用作非住宅用途 (如營商、貨倉等)<br />\n虛報物業（如沒有申報擁有物業等）<br />\n虛報入息（如沒有申報或少報入息等）<br />\n虛報資產（如沒有申報或少報資產等）<br />\n虛報其他資料（如婚姻、家庭狀況等）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.housingauthority.gov.hk/tc/global-elements/contact-us/online-form-for-reporting-abuse-of-public-housing-resources/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.housingauthority.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fglobal-elements%2Fcontact-us%2Fonline-form-for-reporting-abuse-of-public-housing-resources%2Findex.html&d=77sZY8L1Q3njiwGc8u9yTrP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=c03ccae4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.housingauthority.gov.hk/tc/global-elements/contact-us/online-form-for-reporting-abuse-of-public-housing-resources/index.html</a>"},{"pid":"7fbbf65f101f372ab3e03616ee3e1c0bdfdc262f","tid":1181061,"uid":55917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T10:14:37.000Z","msg":"除左派錢"},{"pid":"d5879fdb10bf93653196b79362a0c13e1cb3fbd6","tid":1181061,"uid":30882,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7fbbf65f101f372ab3e03616ee3e1c0bdfdc262f","tid":1181061,"uid":55917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T10:14:37.000Z","msg":"除左派錢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T10:19:43.000Z","msg":"share 翻正苦黎緊好多都會轉哂做 網上表<br />\n<br />\n利申:屌佢我都仲未收到4000啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就黎無錢開飯"},{"pid":"748bca94a1360f0ee09cbef68babcc3b57e6a087","tid":1181061,"uid":222803,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T10:38:24.000Z","msg":"上次見人住公屋揸Maserati<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f7ad54c3ef24c94769652a023441ea8a1c46c01","tid":1181061,"uid":195334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T14:44:55.000Z","msg":"幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}